%-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------%
This folder contains the files (matlab and julia) for Project 6 (2D Wave Equation) in the book
"An Introduction to Element-based Galerkin Methods on Tensor-Product Bases: Analysis, Algorithms, and Applications"
by Francis X. Giraldo

The directory:
For_Students contains the files that the students should have in order to do the project.
For_Instructors contains the solutions (without convergence rates).
A sample Project description is given in the PDF Project6.pdf

You can reach the author by writing to him at frank.giraldo@gmail.com
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------%
